ca.cgjennings.ui

Class BrowserPanel.DefaultViewProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.cgjennings.ui.BrowserPanel.DefaultViewProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BrowserPanel.ViewProvider
    Enclosing class:
    BrowserPanel

    public static class BrowserPanel.DefaultViewProvider
extends Object
implements BrowserPanel.ViewProvider
    A default view provider implementation. This is the fallback provider that is used when no custom provider is set and no better built-in provider is suitable. It provides a basic level of HTML support between HTML 3.2 and HTML 4. It is not generally suited to displaying modern Web sites, but is fine for displaying basic marked-up documentation.
